{"tid":107371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【估國家】17歲少女網上舉報被親父糟蹋4年。","createTime":"2017-02-04T12:24:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T12:49:05.000Z","uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5534ba1717e0f858ac4ea0d2839c544fc584f0e","tid":107371,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:24:11.000Z","msg":"江西小竹妹妹網上貼照片<br />\n<br />\n13歲開始遭父親強姦4年不敢報警揭發。<br />\n<br />\n江西的小竹妹妹自曝從13歲開始，就被禽獸父親強姦，直到17歲。由於受到父親的言語威脅，以及考慮到父親是家裡唯一的經濟來源，所以一直沒報警。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.read.html5.qq.com/image?imageUrl=http%3A%2F%2Finews%2Egtimg%2Ecom%2Fnewsapp%5Fmatch%2F0%2F1101326879%2F0&amp;src=read&amp;t=0&amp;w=320&amp;h=280&amp;q=6&amp;rspimgflag=0&amp;imgflag=15&amp;filesize=55205&amp;referUrl=http%3A%2F%2Fkuaibao%2Eqq%2Ecom%2Fs%2F20170204A059Q000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.read.html5.qq.com%2Fimage%3FimageUrl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Finews%252Egtimg%252Ecom%252Fnewsapp%255Fmatch%252F0%252F1101326879%252F0%26src%3Dread%26t%3D0%26w%3D320%26h%3D280%26q%3D6%26rspimgflag%3D0%26imgflag%3D15%26filesize%3D55205%26referUrl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fkuaibao%252Eqq%252Ecom%252Fs%252F20170204A059Q000&h=e80c907d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.read.html5.qq.com/image?imageUrl=http%3A%2F%2Finews%2Egtimg%2Ecom%2Fnewsapp%5Fmatch%2F0%2F1101337855%2F0&amp;src=read&amp;t=0&amp;w=320&amp;h=326&amp;q=6&amp;rspimgflag=0&amp;imgflag=15&amp;filesize=53968&amp;referUrl=http%3A%2F%2Fkuaibao%2Eqq%2Ecom%2Fs%2F20170204A059Q000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.read.html5.qq.com%2Fimage%3FimageUrl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Finews%252Egtimg%252Ecom%252Fnewsapp%255Fmatch%252F0%252F1101337855%252F0%26src%3Dread%26t%3D0%26w%3D320%26h%3D326%26q%3D6%26rspimgflag%3D0%26imgflag%3D15%26filesize%3D53968%26referUrl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fkuaibao%252Eqq%252Ecom%252Fs%252F20170204A059Q000&h=ab44f03d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.read.html5.qq.com/image?im